WHITE_LABEL_ENABLED=true
DEFAULT_BRAND_NAME=zDash
DEFAULT_BRAND_LOGO_URL=
DEFAULT_BRAND_PRIMARY_COLOR=#7c3aed
DEFAULT_BRAND_ACCENT_COLOR=#22c55e

ONBOARDING_ENABLED=true
CUSTOMER_SUCCESS_ENABLED=true

EnterpriseLicense fields:
id, organization_id, license_key_hash, status, tier, seats, features,
expires_at, offline_mode, issued_to, metadata, created_at, updated_at

BrandingSettings fields:
id, organization_id, workspace_id, brand_name, logo_url, primary_color,
accent_color, support_email, custom_domain, metadata, created_at, updated_at

ExportBundle fields:
id, organization_id, workspace_id, export_type, status, file_path,
include_audit_logs, include_content, include_backtests, include_scheduler,
include_secrets, created_by, created_at, completed_at

OnboardingChecklist fields:
organization_id, workspace_id, completed_steps, pending_steps, progress_percent, updated_at

License service:
- get_license_status(organization_id)
- apply_license(organization_id, license_key)
- validate_license(organization_id)
- revoke_license(organization_id)

Rules:
- Store only license hash.
- Offline license mode supported.
- Invalid license must not disable free/core safe mode.
- License cannot disable production safety lock.

Branding service:
- get_branding(organization_id, workspace_id)
- update_branding(organization_id, workspace_id, patch)
- reset_branding(organization_id, workspace_id)

Rules:
- Tenant scoped.
- Validate color values.
- Never allow script injection in branding fields.

Export service:
- create_export_bundle(request)
- get_export_bundle(bundle_id)
- list_export_bundles()
- import_bundle(file)

Rules:
- Secrets excluded by default.
- include_secrets requires admin and explicit typed confirmation:
  CONFIRM_SECRET_EXPORT
- Export tenant-scoped.
- Export audit event required.

Onboarding service:
- get_checklist(organization_id, workspace_id)
- mark_step_complete(step)
- reset_checklist()
- get_customer_health()

Default onboarding steps:
- create organization
- create workspace
- invite team
- verify risk guardian
- run first dry-run scan
- run first backtest
- create first content item
- review scheduler jobs
- configure billing
- review production safety check

Enterprise API:
GET  /api/enterprise/status
GET  /api/enterprise/license
POST /api/enterprise/license/apply
POST /api/enterprise/license/revoke
GET  /api/enterprise/branding
PATCH /api/enterprise/branding
POST /api/enterprise/branding/reset
GET  /api/enterprise/exports
POST /api/enterprise/exports
GET  /api/enterprise/exports/{bundle_id}
GET  /api/enterprise/onboarding
POST /api/enterprise/onboarding/complete-step
POST /api/enterprise/onboarding/reset
GET  /api/enterprise/customer-health

Rules:
- Auth required.
- Tenant scoped.
- Branding requires owner/admin/operator.
- License apply/revoke requires admin/owner.
- Export requires enterprise entitlement.
- Export with secrets requires admin and confirmation.
- All actions audited.
- Error codes:
  LICENSE_INVALID
  EXPORT_NOT_ALLOWED
  TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED
  FEATURE_NOT_ENTITLED

Events:
enterprise.license.applied
enterprise.license.revoked
enterprise.branding.updated
enterprise.export.started
enterprise.export.completed
enterprise.export.failed
enterprise.onboarding.step.completed

Validation:
cd backend
source .venv/bin/activate
python -m ruff check app tests
python -B -m pytest -q

